Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.72,0:02:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs20}Loveling雨傘  8000日元（含稅）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.31,0:03:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工去吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.80,0:03:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}請看著我\N中島秀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.29,0:03:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要讓我幫他實現這個願望嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.83,0:03:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不知道這個人在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.65,0:03:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}招聘家庭教師\N輔導對象為\N初中一年級的男生\N有意者請聯繫中島
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我是中島
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.86,0:03:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了  我是來應聘家教的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.21,0:03:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  您好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.70,0:03:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.17,0:03:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把話先說在前頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的目標可不是什麼八十神高中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因為馬上就能來進行輔導的人只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.34,0:03:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我只是在看著你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.61,0:03:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.94,0:04:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.11,0:04:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.43,0:04:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來得真晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.86,0:04:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  稍微有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.86,0:04:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8月10日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.78,0:04:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道鳴上悠在做家庭教師的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託他參與看孩子的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他隨口就答應了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這份工作卻會給他帶來更加嚴酷的試煉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.44,0:04:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此時的他還對此一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.57,0:04:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你弄壞的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.79,0:04:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.97,0:04:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太把我的「Neo Feather Man」機器人弄壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒弄壞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.33,0:04:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.35,0:04:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.37,0:04:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停下  吵架是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.07,0:04:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個已經徹底壞掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
