Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.09,0:04:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不是我弄壞的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.59,0:05:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是非常抱…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.08,0:05:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我來賠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.27,0:05:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.29,0:05:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是我弄壞的
